### 更新群组 [PUT /api/groups/{_groupId}]

必须为群组创建者或者组织管理员

+ Parameters
    + _groupId (ObjectId) - 群组 id

+ Attributes
    + name (string) - 群组名称

+ Request

        {
            "name": "Y"
        }

+ Response 200

        {
            "name": "Y",
            "updated": "2016-11-15T08:45:40.977Z",
            "_id": "582acb3487e24e9c95d72e80",
            "pinyin": "y",
            "py": "y"
        }

